SIMPLE: illimitable
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Illimitable
<hw>Il*lim"it*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>il-</ets> not + <ets>limitable</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>illimitable</ets>.]</ety> <def>Incapable of being limited or
bounded; immeasurable; limitless; boundless; <as>as,
<ex>illimitable</ex> space</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The wild, the irregular, the <qex>illimitable</qex>, and the
luxuriant, have their appropriate force of beauty.</q> <rj><qau>De
Quincey.</qau></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Boundless; limitless; unlimited; unbounded;
immeasurable; infinite; immense; vast.</syn></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Il*lim"it*a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Il*lim"it*a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Illimitation</ent>⟦br⟧
